    "en": {
      "title": "08 who went by boat died in India",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "08 people belonging to 03 families residing in Jaffna and Trincomalee were taken into custody by the Tamil Nadu Police yesterday (21st) when they arrived in the Dhanushkodi sea area of \u200b\u200bIndia in a small boat.",
        "It is reported that 03 men, 02 women and 3 children belonging to 03 families have sailed to Dhanushkodi coast of India along the Mannar sea border.",
        "The Tamil Nadu Police have quarantined the people who came to Dhanushkodi and taken steps for further investigation.",
        "The Indian security forces further point out that more than 140 people have gone to India through the coasts of the northern province since the 22nd of March and 130 people have taken refuge in that country.",
        "The Navy also says that nearly 600 people attempted to go abroad without permission and were taken into the custody of the Navy between January and July alone."
      ],
